# graphify-out/ is regenerated locally by the post-commit hook, so it stays local.
# Track only the human-readable report snapshot; graph.json/graph.html are 1MB+
# regenerable artifacts (per-commit churn + machine-absolute-path noise).
#
# Whitelist style: ignore everything, then re-include just the two files we keep.
# Robust against new generated dirs (dated dirs, wiki/, obsidian/, cache/).
*
!/.gitignore
!/GRAPH_REPORT.md
